The Nurse Doesn't Know She Is A Demon | Full Movie | Horror Thriller | Night of the Caregiver

Hospice nurse Julia is hired to be a caregiver for Lillian Gresham, who lives in an isolated house in a remote area. Although she is terminally ill, the elderly Lillian is a cordial and sweet lady. However, as the night goes on, Julia suspects someone or something demonic is also dwelling in the house causing her and Lillian to be in grave danger.

2023. Stars: Natalie Denise Sperl, Eileen Dietz, Anna Oris
